data.description: Perfectly located near downtown Sparks, this spacious home offers open living areas with a large separate family room and a bonus room. The kitchen is updated with appliances included, and a dining/living room combo at the front of the house. The home has large windows bringing in plenty of natural light into the living spaces. The front yard is landscaped for low maintenance, and the large backyard includes a dog run, RV parking, and space for opportunity of your choosing. The property is close to I-80, shopping, food, and parks. The backyard is fully fenced in and has multiple areas for gardening, a covered patio, and a storage shed. The backyard gets a lot of shade, and has space for additional parking.
